ENGINE
1) Create a generic Controller class, which is instanced by Entities (and updated by World through its update function performed on its list of game world Entities)
2) Create a PhysicsController class and begin simple dynamics simulation

RENDERING
1) Create a threaded Texture loader, which creates an additional OpenGL context for loading textures into GPU memory
2) Create an AnimationController and begin doing animated PNG loading and playing

CONTENT
1) Create a Property List loader, which can read generic property lists and update resources with them
2) Flesh out the world loader and world saver with some entities
